{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Arrive in Time&quot; is a minimalist casual strategy game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your goal is to drive a car and collect stars within the time limit to pass each level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">119 different levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Estimated playtime: 4-8 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">support keyboard&amp;mouse and controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gradual difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimalist, relaxed vibe</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Simple Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are only two types of actions in the game: pressing the gas pedal and using cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can play the entire game using just one mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/p1.gif?t=1733193399\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Using Cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to turn left, turn right, or accelerate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Timing is crucial, so don't waste any card.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress through the game, you'll acquire more cards and items to help you solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/p4.gif?t=1733193399\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Follow the Rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't crash into other cars or people, and obey the rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features various obstacles that players need to navigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you advance through levels, more new mechanics will be introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/p3.gif?t=1733193399\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Beware of Night Driving</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's said that in some areas, drivers become tense when driving at night\u2014to the point of losing consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, try to stay in well-lit areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perhaps buying a &quot;Ghost Detector&quot; from the shop might help you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071060/extras/p5.gif?t=1733193399\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Get License","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Nightshift Alone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Through the Oldtown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Too Many People","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Faster Than a Ghost","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Finally Off Work","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Be Patient","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Eco-Friendly","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3071060/aa67589252d1b832b0c25d111213c34ac325605a.jpg"},{"name":"Underground","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommuni